_______________________________________________________________________________
"Awe"
 
        This temporarily increases the psionicist's personal magnetism by a
        large margin.  Adds an amount of charisma dependent on guild
        level for a short length of time.  It is mostly useful for
        obtaining better prices when selling treasure, but with some
        planning it is possible to immediately regenerate the cost of
        the spell before the effects wear off, thus increasing your
        spell points for a short while.  You'll have to be fast and have
        a good plan to accomplish this, however. 
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  awe
